{"tid":298029,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"鐵血的孤兒:長井龍雪推翻古荻莉亞與阿特拉同性結婚論變為收養阿特拉與曉","createTime":"2017-06-26T03:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T04:47:31.000Z","uid":19232,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"991d72fe293d6d86b75e181df128d133cdfcf51a","tid":298029,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/grjYQtF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgrjYQtF.jpg&h=75617f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0RLOARZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0RLOARZ.jpg&h=c8c77b9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這部動畫在第二季的問題主要是設定上有點難以自圓其說，甚至是兩季動畫的一些角色設定方面產生了衝突和落差，雖然在大結局鐵華團的核心戰力全部便當，還剩下的團員過上了平凡的生活，三日月還留下了一個自己的孩子「曉」，之前在發售活動中Bandai方面的主持人稱古荻莉亞與阿特拉同性結婚撫養三日月孩子，而長井龍雪在訪談中推翻了這個說法，稱是古荻莉亞收養了阿特拉與曉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.acgdoge.net/archives/18757\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.acgdoge.net%2Farchives%2F18757&d=QXPzg7KFaPO1RB7uCK5ohpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=4dcd9f14\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.acgdoge.net/archives/18757</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://anihatsu.com/archives/70407683.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fanihatsu.com%2Farchives%2F70407683.html&d=QXPzg7KFaPO1RB7uCK5ohpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=6b999201\" target=\"_blank\">http://anihatsu.com/archives/70407683.html</a><br />\n<br />\n在今年4 月的發售活動上，Bandai方面的主持人稱「在鐵血孤兒的世界中同性是可以結婚的，三日月與阿特拉的孩子全名叫曉&middot;奧格斯&middot;米科斯塔&middot;伯恩斯坦（後三個名字是三日月、阿特拉、古荻莉亞的姓），阿特拉與古荻莉亞最後是結婚了，曉是作為阿特拉與古荻莉亞的孩子，西諾和亞馬基也可以結婚」，而在長井龍雪的鐵血孤兒訪談中，長井龍雪提到「阿特拉、古荻莉亞、曉最後在一起生活沒有正確的設定，是古荻莉亞收養了阿特拉與曉這樣的印象（クーデリアがアトラと暁を養子縁組しているというイメージ），鐵血孤兒動畫中的世界和我們的世界在倫理觀方面稍微有些不同，如果有著違和感想像這個產生不同的理由或許也挺有意思的，不涉及社會倫理和宗教倫理的話，也看不到這個倫理觀差異，但是在動畫中事實上也有描寫宗教觀，這種比較難的部分」"},{"pid":"a18679f23a551eacc5b51121efaa9791441520cc","tid":298029,"uid":9141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:16:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"875d0d3da4d7f49346ac815e5ea8f1c35e5ae8e7","tid":298029,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:18:11.000Z","msg":"屌多幾獲就有份"},{"pid":"fabf0261030640c0d7a60a54281873b43e686219","tid":298029,"uid":6422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"停手啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4457a20896abaee75a8e51a1da2b4f648a5e64dd","tid":298029,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:40:17.000Z","msg":"完啦好麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b209023137809a2b814fb6b47c52e445fcc43f3","tid":298029,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GctpnBV.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGctpnBV.gifv&h=0a3043d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d60936cb4180d25ef7c45d4ae0808097e041dd8","tid":298029,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GctpnBV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGctpnBV.gif&h=11f5881a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0c1661d4badf27a7dc2bd2d48d106b353250bef7","tid":298029,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:30:45.000Z","msg":"想兜到幾時？"},{"pid":"82bc0bede2e4826255d662c5e941299e5017a95a","tid":298029,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:36:03.000Z","msg":"但佢肯撚定唔係超一流機師<br />\n仍然都會俾支針射到希巴爛"},{"pid":"325628a72df46d882d1ce0534b2f6e6671ced6b5","tid":298029,"uid":35373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感覺班撚屌想靠binc炒熱番套野 大家唔好中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台主都係想靠轉貼佢黎炒熱自己